(10, 'Trading Account Types', '<section class="content-box">\r\n<h2>Trading Account Types</h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border: none; border-radius: 4px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;">In becoming a client with&nbsp;House of Borse, it&rsquo;s the beginning of a solid partnership that we take seriously. House of Borse accounts are empowered with the necessary tools to consolidate your trading expertise. But the first step is to choose which one of the three trading accounts types that will suit&nbsp;your investments. House of Borse Accounts provide traders with multiple tools and have the best overview to the markets before taking action. Every trading decision counts!</p>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="header_with_stars">\r\n<h2 class="f-primary-b">ACCOUNT HOLDER BENEFITS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p class="b-infoblock-description f-desc-section f-center">By choosing one of our accounts traders have access to:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="b-hr-stars f-hr-stars ">\r\n<div class="b-hr-stars__group"><span class="fa fa-star">&nbsp;</span> <span class="fa fa-star">&nbsp;</span> <span class="fa fa-star">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="text_title" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(178, 165, 120); text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 22.1px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><img id="membership_inner_logo_img" src="/cms_assets/houseofborse/img/Logo_Footer.svg" />\r\n<ul class="membership_inner_list">\r\n	<li>Available One click trading (OCT)</li>\r\n	<li>Minimum lot size of 0.10 lot</li>\r\n	<li>No limits for the maximum lots per single trade&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The possibilities to use the MT4 System Trade Expert</li>\r\n	<li>Allowed Scalping</li>\r\n	<li>NDD, ECN Execution</li>\r\n	<li>Direct ac