(11, 'Interest Free Accounts', '\r\n<h2>Interest Free Accounts</h2>\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">The Interest Free Account will be charged a daily management fee applicable for positions held open with House of Borse beyond the close of business day (&quot;Management Fee&quot;). Note, this will apply only to a contract or product which is not a future.&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">In the event the Client&#39;s position(s) are rolled into the next business day, then the Client shall be charged the Management Fee from the date the position(s) was/were opened and on a daily basis for each day, including weekend, until the position(s) with House of Borse is/are closed.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Management Fee on all account types are subject to change at any time. House of Borse reserves the right to revoke the Interest Free Account in its sole discretion at any time. Corporate accounts are not eligible for this interest free option.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Management Fee</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: 